pullRequest.body:
While many of the lemmas cease to apply,
the definitions of sequences and their sums are still perfectly well-behaved in additive monoids; no negation is needed.

---

If this PR depends on other PRs, please list them below this comment,
using the following format:

- [ ] depends on: #xyz [optional extra text]
-->

In future, we could use this to generalize `NormedSpace.exp` such that it works with `NNReal`, but unless leanprover-community/mathlib#16554 or #11203 lands and provides a `DivisionSemiring.nnqsmul` field, that would conflict with #8370.

EDIT(Ya√´l): #11203 landed.
